## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="114c4-102">A<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder>控件在主页面中，定义内容的相对区域并呈现所有文本、 标记和服务器控件从相关<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content>在内容页中找到的控件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="114c4-102">A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder> control defines a relative region for content in a master page, and renders all text, markup, and server controls from a related <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content> control found in a content page.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="114c4-103">A<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content>与关联控件<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder>使用其<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content.ContentPlaceHolderID%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="114c4-103">A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content> control is associated with a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder> using its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content.ContentPlaceHolderID%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="114c4-104">设置<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content.ContentPlaceHolderID%2A>属性的值<xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A>将相关属性<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder>在母版页中的控件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="114c4-104">Set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content.ContentPlaceHolderID%2A> property to the value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A> property of the related <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder> control in a master page.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="114c4-105">多个<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder>可以在母版页中声明。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="114c4-105">More than one <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder> can be declared in a master page.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="114c4-106">在内容页中，只有一个<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content>控件可以提供的内容<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder>母版页中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="114c4-106">Within a content page, only one <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content> control can supply the content for a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder> in the master page.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="114c4-107">但是，在每个使用母版页的内容页，你可以单独<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content>与关联的控件<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="114c4-107">However, in each content page that uses a master page, you can have separate <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content> controls associated with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="114c4-108">例如，你可以定义<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder>页标题在母版页中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="114c4-108">For example, you can define the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder> for the page title in a master page.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="114c4-109">对于每个使用母版页的内容页，你可以添加<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content>提供文本和页标题的标记的控件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="114c4-109">For each content page that uses the master page, you can add a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content> control that supplies the text and markup for the page title.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="114c4-110">XHTML 的符合性，如果标题未定义或无法找到，则创建空的标题元素。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="114c4-110">For XHTML compliance, an empty title element is created if a title has not been defined or cannot be found.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="114c4-111">你可以指定默认内容放在<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder>控制标记，但此内容替换为关联的内容页中的任何内容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="114c4-111">You can specify default content placed within the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder> control tags, but this content is replaced by any content in an associated content page.</span></span>  
  
